snippet.title: Age of Empires III - E3 2005 Trailer
snippet.description:
It's the dawn of a new age in real-time strategy games. A brave New World is rising -- a hostile yet beautiful world, filled with innovative gameplay, new strategic scenarios, eye-searing graphics and much more. Welcome to a world called Age of Empires III.

Robot Entertainment continues to support the community of Age of Empires III players at AgeCommunity.com
